cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_msg1_FDM to 10 (valid range 0-3) will cause configuration validation failure and prevent RACH procedure initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_msg1_FDM 設定為 10（有效範圍 0-3）會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止 RACH 程序初始化。
